{"route":{"route":"/page/6/","outputPath":"page/6/index.html","kind":"home","title":"Asutorufaのブログ - Page 6","language":"ja","params":{"page":"6"}},"description":"こんにちは","posts":[{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/安卓使用dalvikvm运行java(termux运行java).md","route":"/posts/8b98169e/","abbrlink":"8b98169e","title":"安卓使用dalvikvm运行java(termux运行java)","date":"2019-02-02 23:02:35","updated":"2019-02-02 23:02:35","tags":["android","java"],"categories":["android"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>一直想要使用termux来在安卓上写java,但termux上只有ecj可以使java编译为目标文件class,却不能使其编译为可执行文件<br>\n发现通过安卓自带的dalvikvm可以运行,只是步骤繁琐一些</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装所需工具\">安装所需工具</h2>\n<p>termux上安装 ecj 和 dx就可以了</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">apt install ecj dx</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"编译为class文件\">编译为class文件</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">ecj XXX.java</span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"8b98169e","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/用CIDR表示网段.md","route":"/posts/e2b25bb8/","abbrlink":"e2b25bb8","title":"用CIDR表示网段","date":"2019-02-02 22:34:07","updated":"2019-02-02 22:34:07","tags":["IP","CIDR"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>我们知道一般CIDR(无类别域间路由)网段的表示为:<strong>192.168.0.0/24</strong>这种形式</p>\n<h2 id=\"ip地址\">IP地址</h2>\n<p>首先我们得知道ip地址是如何来的<br>\nipv4的地址是用32位二进制数表示的<br>\n如: 255.255.255.0 -&gt; 11111111.11111111.11111111.00000000</p>\n<h2 id=\"网络前缀\">网络前缀</h2>\n<p><strong>192.168.0.0/24</strong>中的24就是网络前缀,网络前缀可转化为网络掩码,24表示网络掩码的前24位为1</p>\n<h2 id=\"网络掩码\">网络掩码</h2>\n<p>「网络掩码」又叫「子网掩码」、「地址掩码」、「子網路遮罩」（subnet mask），它是一种用来指明一个IP地址的哪些位标识的是主机所在的网络地址以及哪些位标识的是主机地址的位掩码。      --维基百科</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"e2b25bb8","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/android-dumpsys-tool.md","route":"/posts/25303996/","abbrlink":"25303996","title":"android dumpsys tool","date":"2019-02-01 00:00:02","updated":"2019-02-01 00:00:02","tags":["android","adb"],"categories":["android"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>查看dumpsys所有的子命令:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">dumpsys | grep <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;DUMP OF SERVICE&quot;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>output:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE SurfaceFlinger:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE accessibility:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE account:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE activity:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE alarm:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE appwidget:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE audio:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE backup:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE battery:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE batteryinfo:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE clipboard:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE connectivity:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE content:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE cpuinfo:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE device_policy:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE devicestoragemonitor:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE diskstats:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE dropbox:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE entropy:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE hardware:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE input_method:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE iphonesubinfo:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE isms:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE location:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE media.audio_flinger:</span></span><span cla