</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE power:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">37</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE reboot:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">38</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE screenshot:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">39</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE search:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">40</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE sensor:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">41</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE simphonebook:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">42</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE statusbar:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">43</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE telephony.registry:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">44</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE throttle:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">45</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE usagestats:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">46</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE vibrator:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">47</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE wallpaper:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">48</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE wifi:</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">49</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">DUMP OF SERVICE window:</span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"25303996","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/安卓通过shell更改语言.md","route":"/posts/f7f814df/","abbrlink":"f7f814df","title":"安卓通过shell更改语言","date":"2019-01-23 19:15:44","updated":"2019-01-23 19:15:44","tags":["android"],"categories":["android"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>对于Android M或更高版本，使用：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">setprop ro.product.locale xx-XX</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">setprop persist.sys.locale xx-XX</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>xx是语言<br>\nXX是国家<br>\n改为日语为:xx=ja XX=JP</p>\n<p>其他安卓版本:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">setprop persist.sys.language xx</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">setprop persist.sys.country XX</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">setprop ctl.restart zygote</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>xx是语言<br>\nXX是国家</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"f7f814df","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/解决xfce4画面撕裂.md","route":"/posts/38868ade/","abbrlink":"38868ade","title":"解决xfce4画面撕裂","date":"2018-12-09 00:04:38","updated":"2018-12-09 00:04:38","tags":["linux","xfce4"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<h2 id=\"安装compton\">安装compton</h2>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> apt install compton</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"修改配置文件\">修改配置文件</h2>\n<p>compton的配置文件在~/.config/compton.conf<br>\n因为有些窗口的阴影有时候会变的很奇怪,大概你有可能需要修改一下,附上我的:</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"38868ade","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/linux下intel-AMD双显卡切换.md","route":"/posts/3b8b96de/","abbrlink":"3b8b96de","title":"linux下intel&AMD双显卡切换","date":"2018-09-08 19:02:47","updated":"2020-05-05 19:02:47","tags":["linux","双显卡","amd"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>使用<strong>xrandr</strong>显示可支持的显卡</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">xrandr --listproviders</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>输出类似以下内容</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">Providers: number : 2</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">Provider 0: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">id</span>: 0x6b <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cap</span>: 0x9, Source Output, Sink Offload crtcs: 3 outputs: 7 associated providers: 1 name:modesetting</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">Provider 1: <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">id</span>: 0x41 <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cap</span>: 0x6, Sink Output, Source Offload crtcs: 2 outputs: 0 associated providers: 1 name:OLAND @ pci:0000:01:00.0</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>To be able to render GPU-intensive applications by the more powerful discrete card use</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">xrandr --setprovideroffloadsink 1 0</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>或者</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"3b8b96de","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/python使用lxml分析网页.md","route":"/posts/77d15527/","abbrlink":"77d15527","title":"python使用lxml分析网页","date":"2018-08-07 14:47:51","updated":"2018-08-07 14:47:51","tags":["python","编程"],"categories":["python"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>首先得引入lxml</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#xpath为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">frome lxml <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> etree</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector为</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> lxml.html</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#cssselector使用起来简单但功能比xpath少</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>cssselector</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">tree = lxml.html.fromstring(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;你获取的网页源代码文件或变量&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css = tree.cssselect(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要选择的内容&#x27;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#例如tree.cssselect(&#x27;div.word-info &gt; div.pronounces &gt; span.word-audio&#x27;)</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#选择器选择的结果为list</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.text_content()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#表示选择的内容</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">css.attrib[<span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;要表示的标签属性&#x27;</span>]</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">#如css.attrb[&#x27;class&#x27;]表示的就是所选择内容的class属性</span></span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"77d15527","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/python获取网页源码-爬虫.md","route":"/posts/cee10602/","abbrlink":"cee10602","title":"python获取网页源码(爬虫?)","date":"2018-08-07 14:35:06","updated":"2018-08-07 14:35:06","tags":["python","编程"],"categories":["python"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>利用requrst,使用首先要 使用方法</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"cee10602","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/snap删除旧的core-snap删除其他版本的软件.md","route":"/posts/b6b8953/","abbrlink":"b6b8953","title":"snap删除旧的core(snap删除其他版本的软件)","date":"2018-06-28 13:43:41","updated":"2018-06-28 13:43:41","tags":["linux","snap"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<p>偶尔发现snap会自动升级core且不删除旧版，在’/snap/core’ 会发现好几个版本的文件夹。 使用 删除某个版本的core，xxx是软件的rev，使用 可以查看软件的rev，其他软件也能用这个方法删除旧的版本哦。 参考：How to unmount and possibly delete old Ubuntu Core snap</p>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"b6b8953","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false},{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/ubuntu终端下连接wifi.md","route":"/posts/fb6d8628/","abbrlink":"fb6d8628","title":"ubuntu终端下连接wifi","date":"2018-06-23 12:24:10","updated":"2018-06-23 12:24:10","tags":["linux"],"categories":["linux"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"<h2 id=\"首先使用rfkill查看你的wifi设备是否被停用\">首先使用rfkill查看你的wifi设备是否被停用</h2>\n<p>使用命令</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">rfkill list</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>获得设备列表，每个都包含与之关联的索引号，从 0 开始<br>\n查看设备是否被停用，要启用被停用的设备，请运行：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">rfkill unblock &lt;索引号&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>要启用所有设备，请运行：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">rfkill unblock all</span></span></code></pre>\n","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[],"slugForSearch":"fb6d8628","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}]}